She tranformed into bot mode and got up to her knees. Se drew a small 
hand gun and fired at Razopas.  She got up and limped towards the 
base, holding her neck.  She now had two woounds to the neck and the 
acid was eating her armor away quickly.  She limped over as fast as 
she could to the base.  She hobbled past Airbomber.
